xis represents the mean predicted probability, while the y-axis represents the observ\hich\af0\dbch\af31505\loch\f0 ed fraction\hich\af0\dbch\af31505\loch\f0  of positives. Accompanying histograms \hich\af0\dbch\af31505\loch\f0 (
\hich\af0\dbch\af31505\loch\f0 bottom) \hich\af0\dbch\af31505\loch\f0 illustrate the distribution of predicted probabilities for each technique.}{\rtlch\fcs1 \ai\af0\afs16 \ltrch\fcs0 \i\fs16\cf23\insrsid10099738 
