ecessary but not sufficient requirement to be used in clinical practice; it needs to be recalibrated on out-of-distribution groups such as female soccer, male basketball and gymnastics cohorts.}{\rtlch\fcs1 \ai\af0\afs20 \ltrch\fcs0 
